# Data Cleaning & Visualization Project

## Objective

The objective of this project is to clean, process, and visualize data using Python libraries.

## Dataset Used

Sales Dataset (CSV format)

## Tools and Libraries Used

* Python
* Pandas
* Matplotlib
* Seaborn

## Steps Performed

1. Loaded the dataset using Pandas
2. Checked dataset information
3. Checked missing values
4. Removed duplicate rows
5. Filled missing numerical values
6. Saved cleaned dataset
7. Created visualizations such as histogram and heatmap

## Output

* Cleaned dataset generated successfully
* Histogram visualization created
* Heatmap visualization created

## Conclusion

This project helped in understanding data preprocessing, cleaning techniques, and data visualization using Python.
